                            <comment id="12804530" author="cziegeler" created="Mon, 25 Jan 2010 13:16:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After some debugging I found the problem: the dynamic classloader - the package admin classloader uses a negativ cache: if a class&lt;br/&gt;
is not found, the class name is put into a cache for improved performance.&lt;br/&gt;
However, if a bundle is installed, this cache is not cleared.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Moving this bundle to the dynamic classloader.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12804534" author="cziegeler" created="Mon, 25 Jan 2010 13:33:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Clearing the negative caches now on bundle resolved events - fixed in revision 902807&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
